SummaryPower Corporation of Canada - Strategy, SWOT and Corporate Finance Report, is a source of comprehensive company data and information. The report covers the company's structure, operation, SWOT analysis, product and service offerings and corporate actions, providing a 360Ë view of the company.Power Corporation of Canada (Power Corporation or 'the group') is a diversified international management and holding firm with interests in diverse sectors such as financial services, communications and other businesses. The group's principal controlling asset is Power Financial Corporation (Power Financial), a diversified management and holding company with substantial interests in the financial services sector across Canada, the US, Europe, and Asia, through its controlling interests in Great-West Lifeco (Lifeco) and IGM Financial (IGM). Power Corporation operates in Canada, Europe, and the US. It is headquartered in Montreal, Canada.Scope- Detailed information on Power Corporation of Canada required for business and competitor intelligence needs.- A study of the major internal and external factors affecting Power Corporation of Canada in the form of a SWOT analysis.- An in-depth view of the business model of Power Corporation of Canada including a breakdown and examination of key business segments.- Intelligence on Power Corporation of Canada's mergers and acquisitions (MandA), strategic partnerships and alliances, capital raising, private equity transactions, and financial and legal advisors.- News about Power Corporation of Canada, such as business expansion, restructuring, and contract wins.- Large number of easy-to-grasp charts and graphs that present important data and key trends.Reasons to buy- Gain understanding of Power Corporation of Canada and the factors that influence its strategies.- Track strategic initiatives of the company and latest corporate news and actions.- Assess Power Corporation of Canada as a prospective partner, vendor or supplier.- Support sales activities by understanding your customers' businesses better.- Stay up to date on Power Corporation of Canada's business structure, strategy and prospects.
								

