Corporate Social Responsibility at Power Corporation






Incorporated in 1925, Power Corporation of Canada is a diversified international management and holding company with interests in companies in the financial services, communications and other business sectors in North America, Europe and Asia.
For Power Corporation, Corporate Social Responsibility is best achieved through its long-standing practice of responsible management. Throughout this dedicated website you will find how Power Corporation implements its CSR agenda, both through its commitments and through its actions.







 A Message from our  Co-CEOs













The first responsibility of business is to be profitable and sustainable. We have also long believed that business must also play a role within the broader society in which it operates.







Learn more










United Nations  Global Compact













At Power Corporation, we have strengthened our commitment to responsible management by becoming a signatory to the United Nations Global Compact.







Learn more














To find out more about Power Corporation:






powercorporation.com








